Package pacman_ultimater.project_base.core

Provides core classes and interfaces for usage from application's controllers.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGameOverHandler
    Interface for classes that handle game over request.
    IKeyDownHandler
    Interface for klasses that handle key down action.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClasspathFileReader
    Class handling resource files from classpath reading.
    DefaultAI
    Class providing methods for AI movement and enumerable for easy programmatically recognition of entities.
    Direction
    Class providing data structure for directions via enumerable directionType.
    HighScoreClass
    Class provides high score loading and saving from/to encoded formate in congif file.
    KeyBindings
    Class handling bindings of all the usefull keys.
    LoadMap
    Class that handles manipulation with text files containing map.
    Tile
    Class provides resources for saving text symbols as tiles and easier further manipulation.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DefaultAI.nType
    Enumerable that characterizes all the possible entity's states.
    Direction.directionType
    Enumerable representing possible directions.
    Tile.nType
    Enumerable for possible tile states.
